SUMMARY:Ballroom Dance with Stardusters!
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nNo partner required\, beautiful floor\, lesson included\, friendly dancers. Typical attendance is 1-2 MeetUp people and 45-60 general public. Plenty of people to meet and dance with!\n\nStardusters is a local non-profit that hosts ballroom dances every second Saturday. Join us!\n\n### **-Masks are optional.**\n\n* **The CDC says the best way to minimize the chance of covid infection is to have circulating fresh air. We will open windows and run fans to get as close to this ideal as we can.**\n* **Admission is $15\, cash or check.**\n* **As always\, we provide a printed playlist of all songs together with the recommended dance.**\n* General dancing after the lesson will include all ballroom dances plus selections of Salsa\, Bachata\, Country 2 Step\, Night Club 2 Step and West Coast Swing\n* **Water and a small selection of snacks will be provided.**\n* **No partner needed.**\n\n## **The Century Center 100 North Greensboro Street\, Carrboro\, NC**\n\n**Click here to see a map of recommended parking areas: [Parking Areas](https://www.townofcarrboro.org/DocumentCenter/View/6718/CC-Color-Parking-Map)**\n\n# **Free Dance Lesson from 7:20-8:15**\n\n# **Ballroom Dancing from 8:15 - 10:40 PM**\n\n# **$15 admission**\n\n**Free Refreshments**\n\n## **[Visit and Like Us on Facebook](http://www.facebook.com/trianglestardusters.org) https://www.facebook.com/trianglestardusters.org**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/raleigh-triangle-activities/events/313163900/
