SUMMARY:Free Medieval Combat Training (Hillsborough\, NC) - Broadsword - Armor - Rapier
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nLearn the European martial art of broadsword and shield\, wearing steel armor. Or maybe Renaissance dueling with rapier and dagger is more your style. Beginners welcome! No experience necessary. Some loaner armor is available.\n\nRapier instructor: Percival Aldridge\, OD\, OP\nBroadsword instructor: William of Bedford\, KSCA\nAdministrator (KM): Charles Fleming\n*This event is held and managed by the [Canton of Buckston-on-Eno](https://buckston.windmastershill.org)\, a branch of the* [Society for Creative Anachronism\, Inc.](https://welcome.sca.org/) *and is considered the Official channel of this group here. Questions regarding its content should be directed to [chatelaine@buckston.windmastershill.org](http://chatelaine@buckston.windmastershill.org) or to [socialmedia@sca.org.](http://socialmedia@sca.org.) Inclusion of external links does not indicate implicit nor explicit endorsement of any content or products.*
